WebService::Browshot version 1.5.0
================================

Perl extension for Browshot http://www.browshot.com/, a web service to create website screenshots in real-time.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  URI::Encode
  JSON
  LWP::UserAgent

SOURCE

The source code is available on github at https://github.com/juliensobrier/browshot-perl

CPAN

The library is available on CPAN at http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?WebService::Browshot

